  <h1 class="gem-c-title__text gem-c-title__text--long">
    Direction issued to the Chief Regulator of Ofqual
  </h1>
</div>
  </div>
  

  <div class="govuk-grid-column-two-thirds">
    
  <p class="gem-c-lead-paragraph">Directions from Gavin Williamson MP, Secretary of State for Education, to Sally Collier, Chief Regulator of Ofqual, about awarding results for qualifications being assessed for summer 2020.</p>

  </div>
</div>

